data.title: Requirements
contents: You need to have the Admin Permission on the Server
The bot needs to be able to read in that Channel
Best case: beeing able to delete messages

data.title: What happens then?
contents: I'll sync all your Channels with the RLTracker backend
Next i'll send you a link to your personal Control Panel
Just set everything up as you need it!

meCard.title: How does !me work?
contents: !me works exactly as !stats and !rankup, but without the player platform and the UserID
I check your Discord account for a connected RLTracker account and when i got this, i have your connected Player Profile

child.title: So what do you have to do?
You connected Discord and Steam, but !me isnt working?

contents.text: Make sure that you are logged into the same account on the browser AND on the App! Then try connecting it again.
